Perform required testing in coordination with evaluator's to develop modified Commercial Off-The-Shelf (COTS) systems to
the warfighter that meet the requirements. This will support Capability Set #2 Milestone C in FY 2028. Continued Program
management and administration processes to include but not limited to program oversight, resource justification, budgeting and
programming, milestone and schedule tracking.
FY 2026 to FY 2027 Increase/Decrease Statement:
Increase in FY 2027 to support Commercial Off-The-Shelf (COTS) Performance Testing scheduled activities.
