- CB Medical Countermeasures (estimated funding, $4.2 Million): Continue development of new therapeutics for viral disease and
initiate development of microphysiological systems to evaluate and accelerate development of medical countermeasures (MCMs).
- CB Detection (estimated funding, $4.0 Million): Continue exploring innovative methods for improved CB threat detection and
manufacturing capabilities with a minimal logistical footprint.
