fielded CB information systems and applications. CB Warning Reporting and Hazard Prediction capabilities and efforts will
be deployed by CSC2 in the FY 2027 - FY 2029 timeframe. Continuous engineering for the currently deployed chemical and
biological (CB) information systems (Joint Effects Model (JEM), Joint Warning and Reporting Network (JWARN), Chemical,
Biological, Radiological, Nuclear (CBRN) Information System (CBRN IS)), and CSC2. The approach to consolidation simplifies
software BA7 management under one line and synchronizes the sunset of JEM and JWARN systems as replacement capabilities
are deployed through CSC2.

