FC ACS), Common Analytical Laboratory System Theater Validation Integrated System (CALS TV IS), Chemical Biological
Radiological Nuclear Dismounted Reconnaissance System (CBRN DRS), Joint Chemical Agent Detector (JCAD) M4A1, M8
Chemical Detection Paper, and Enhanced Maritime Biological Detection (EMBD) programs. MOD SEN benefits the warfighter
by establishing a time phased modernization plan to address equipment obsolescence, system functionality improvements, and
integrate technological advancements.

