Description: This project performs engineering and manufacturing development of the next generation JETS, transitioning
technologies developed in the Precision Targeting and Target Acquisition Development project. The JETS II will be an advanced
precision targeting system incorporating improved target acquisition sensors and optics, improved targeting sensors, targeting
algorithms, and a M-Code GPS receiver while reducing size, weight, and power requirements. It will integrate JETS into the
Adaptive Squad Architecture (ASA) using the Intra Soldier Wireless (ISW) capability.

