D. Acquisition Strategy
The FALCONS Abbreviated Capability Development Document (A-CDD) was approved 23 March 2023. The program was approved by the AAE on 17 November
2023 to proceed with a Mid-Tier Acquisition-Rapid Prototyping (MTA-RP) approach using an Other Transaction Agreement (OTA). FALCONS is currently planning to
award the OTA in 2QFY2025 and finalize a Government performance specification with feedback from the vendors. The program plans to develop the required program
entrance documentation to initiate the Middle Tier of Acquisition Rapid Prototyping effort in FY2026.




